column4: <content>Death of the Virgin. Sources: 1) Schongauer; 2) Hogenberg; 3) Breviarium Grimani. Arias Montanus in letter to Ortelius says that he remembers having seen the picture in his house, see Popham, Ortelius and ex [Johannes] Hessels, [Abrahami Ortelii (geographi Antverpiensis) et virorum eruditorum ad eundem et ad Jacobum Colium Ortelianum (Abrahami Ortelii sororis filium) epistulae... (1524-1628), Cantabrigiae, 1887-1897] note [p. 334 c]  by [Alfred] Scharf in Glück, Aus 3 Jhdten [Aus drei Jahrhunderten europäischer Malerei, Wien: Anton Schroll], dates: 1564.</content>
